Name: Instapaper
Description: I could not live without Instapaper and am happy I paid for the full version. When you're surfing the web and come across something you'd like to read but is too lengty for that moment, with the click of a button it is registered in Instapaper. Later sync it to your mobile device and you will have the content available in a pleasantly readable format, even offline for that long bus trip. Since I read as much as I do online, I have tried Google Reader, delicious etc, and except for that Instapaper becomes less "social", it is the best thing so far.
